OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start for many, then
OL,6,Fbrightening up, but with scattered
OL,7,Fheavy and locally thundery showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping. A rather cool and blustery
OL,9,Fday, but feeling warmer when the sun
OL,10,Fappears, and in shelter.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers becoming less
OL,13,Ffrequent this evening and overnight,
OL,14,Fwith some clear spells developing
OL,15,Facross the region later in the night.
OL,16,FWinds slowly easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
