OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,6,Fshowers are still possible in places.
OL,7,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,9,Ffor the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,12,Fwindy with rain clearing northwards on
OL,13,FSaturday. Brighter with some showers
OL,14,Fon Sunday, then overnight rain
OL,15,Fclearing to brighter, showery weather
OL,16,Fagain on Monday. Feeling warm in the
OL,17,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
